HEADWORD: Sparoid
<hw>Spa"roid</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sparus</ets> the gilthead + <ets>-oid</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>sparo⟦ium⟧de</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining
to the <fam>Sparidae</fam>, a family of spinous-finned fishes which
includes the scup, sheepshead, and sea bream.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>One of the
<fam>Sparidae</fam>.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

